## Three layers (compile insight; do not invent SoR)

| Layer | Location | Rule |
|---|---|---|
| **Raw sources** | ⟨immutable paths / URLs / CLOSEOUT digests⟩ | Read-only — Brain never edits |
| **Compiled insight** | This pool `HIGHLIGHTS.md`, `DIGESTS/`, `PROPOSALS.md`, optional `wiki/`, optional `RESEARCH-INDEX.md` | Brain may append/update **insight only** |
| **Schema** | This charter + [`PERSISTENT-RESEARCH-BRAIN.md`](./PERSISTENT-RESEARCH-BRAIN.md) (or cite-by-path from hive kit) | Admin-owned; agents do not self-expand walls |

