## Admin phrases

| Phrase | Effect |
|---|---|
| `start research loop ⟨pool-id⟩` | Status → `active` (from `admin-locked` or `paused` after removing `PAUSE`) |
| `pause research loop ⟨pool-id⟩` | Create `PAUSE`; status → `paused` |
| `lock research charter ⟨pool-id⟩` | Status → `admin-locked` (ready for validate + first start) |

## Session modes allowed

- [ ] ingest — compile raw → DIGESTS / wiki / index
- [ ] query — answer from compiled insight + cites
- [ ] lint — contradictions / stale / orphans → HIGHLIGHTS or INBOX

